    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Rare find alert \u2014 this is the one you've been waiting for! This car is in absolutely mint condition, presenting like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is flawless with zero blemishes, the interior is pristine and fresh, and everything runs and functions perfectly. If you're looking for a like-new vehicle without the new-car price tag, this is an exceptional opportunity you won't want to miss!",
